timeline.message:
Observer for DNS ServiceDiscoverer

Motivation:

Provides visibility into DNS resolutions behind DNS `ServiceDiscoverer`.

Modifications:

- Add `DnsServiceDiscovererObserver` interface that users can use to
be notified about internal DNS resolutions;
- Add `DefaultDnsServiceDiscovererBuilder#oberser(...)` method to
configure `DnsServiceDiscovererObserver`;
- Improve javadoc;
- Add tests;

Result:

User can get visibility into DNS resolutions.

