replies.bodyText:
Prefixes in the name help when users what a "flatten" version of the interfaces:
class MyObserver implements DnsServiceDiscovererObserver, DnsDiscoveryObserver,
        DnsResolutionObserver {
...
}
If later we will have DnsQueryObserver inside DnsResolutionObserver, without prefixes users won't be able to differentiate onError from one interface from another.

